<paragraph base="F16130711" principles="yes" id="IFRS12_24"><paranum>24</paranum><prolog><data name="standard_number" value="IFRS 12"/><data name="paranum" value="24"/></prolog><body><p id="IFRS12_P0171">An entity shall disclose information that enables users                     of its financial statements:</p><ol base="F16130713" type="lower-alpha" id="IFRS12_L0036"><li><li_value>(a)</li_value>         <p base="F16130714" id="IFRS12_P0172">to understand the nature and extent of its interests in unconsolidated <xref base="F16130768" href="IFRS12_APPA.dita#IFRS12_APPA/IFRS12_DI0003">structured entities<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0358"/></ph></xref> (<xref base="F16228728" href="IFRS12_g26-28.dita#IFRS12_g26-28" id="IFRS12_X0187">paragraphs 26&#x2013;28</xref>); and</p>       </li><li><li_value>(b)</li_value>         <p base="F16130717" id="IFRS12_P0173">to evaluate the nature of, and changes in, the risks associated with its interests in unconsolidated structured entities (<xref base="F16458500" href="IFRS12_g29-31.dita#IFRS12_g29-31" id="IFRS12_X0188">paragraphs 29&#x2013;31</xref>).</p>                </li></ol></body></paragraph>